Subject: [PATCH] Harfbuzz 3.0 support

Based on

- https://github.com/google/skia/third_party/skia/commit/66684b17b382
- https://github.com/google/skia/third_party/skia/commit/51d83abcd24a
- https://github.com/chromium/chromium/commit/b289f6f3fcbc
---
